item.title: META
item.description: score:-150 Chances: Meta stock is trading tightly near a high after the earnings gap-up. Meta Platforms said it will stop paying Australian news publishers for content that appears on Facebook, setting up a fresh battle with Canberra. Among the Magnificent Seven stocks to buy and watch, Apple, Nvidia and Tesla stock are in new buy areas.

item.title: CSCO
item.description: score:22 Chances: Cisco Systems (CSCO) settling at $52.24, representing a -0.1% change from its previous close. Cisco, Microsoft Corp. and Samsung Electronics announced new meeting room solutions for enhanced collaboration experiences. Cisco released its 2024 Data Privacy Benchmark Study, highlighting growing privacy concerns and trust challenges with AI.
